---
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-base-100">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Tagline + Testimonial side by side -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">
        Reduce Your PM Service Times and Increase Asset Reliability
      </h2>
      <p class="prose-body max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        It's no secret that time and effort is often wasted during preventative maintenance servicing and asset inspections. Our platform goes further — delivering a truly paperless, standardised system.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Key benefits as cards instead of wall of text -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="text-primary mb-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="section-subheading">Standardised Processes</h3>
          <p class="prose-body">Eliminate inconsistent processes and communication delays with structured, guided workflows that work regardless of skill level.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="text-primary mb-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="section-subheading">Paperless & Digital</h3>
          <p class="prose-body">Move from paper-based service sheets to mobility-based software. Every defect recorded, every step tracked, nothing lost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card bg-base-200">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="text-primary mb-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.28m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="section-subheading">Proven Results</h3>
          <p class="prose-body">Our platform increases fleet reliability, detects issues early before they become environmental hazards, and improves overall plant performance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <div class="card bg-neutral text-neutral-content max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="card-body items-center text-center p-8 sm:p-10">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary mb-2 opacity-60" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4.583 17.321C3.553 16.227 3 15 3 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179zm10 0C13.553 16.227 13 15 13 13.011c0-3.5 2.457-6.637 6.03-8.188l.893 1.378c-3.335 1.804-3.987 4.145-4.247 5.621.537-.278 1.24-.375 1.929-.311 1.804.167 3.226 1.648 3.226 3.489a3.5 3.5 0 01-3.5 3.5c-1.073 0-2.099-.49-2.748-1.179z"/></svg>
        <blockquote class="text-lg italic mb-3">
          After implementing ZoneMaintenance, within 3 months our culture changed to 'This is how we do maintenance now'. Incredible results.
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="text-sm font-semibold opacity-60 not-italic">
          &mdash; PM Service Bay Superintendent
        </cite>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
